data.description: West Valley Early Mid Century Farmhouse With All The Updates!This 4 bedroom 3 bath property is spacious and inviting. The floor plan provides a convenient flow with a gathering space off the kitchen along with  an oversized living room with gas fireplace, formal dining room, office, laundry and primary bedroom with a main bathroom in it's own wing all on the main level.  The remodeled kitchen boasts new cabinets, appliances, lovely tile work, Carrera stone countertops and new luxury plank flooring.  Both bathrooms on the main level have been remodeled keeping the traditional style of the period.  Original hardwood floors coupled with new living room carpet and LVP.   And what beautiful views!   There are 3 large bedrooms with a full bath upstairs and an unfinished basement with an outside entrance, great for storage and hobbies.  A deck with views of the mountains wraps around the the entire side of the house and off the kitchen. One car attached garaged along with a detached one car garage.  A sought after location nestled back on an extra large lot.  New sprinkler system.  The driveway wraps behind the property with 2 entrances for ease and plenty of parking.  Come take a look at this classic beauty!
